title: SAP HANA: Migration of Statistics Server
agents: linux
catalog: app/sap_hana
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the migration state of SAP HANA statistics server.
 To make this check work you have to install the agent plugin
 {{mk_sap_hana}}.

 State is OK if the migration was succesful.
 State is WARNING if an installation is in progress.
 State is UNKNOWN if the agent plugin returns a non-mappable output.

item:
 The sid instance name

inventory:
 One service is created for each instance.
